Net-BGPdump
===========

Net::BGPdump is a perl binding to libbgpdump.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


SOURCE CODE

The official distribution lives here:

https://tools.netsa.cert.org/confluence/display/tt/Net-BGPdump

The package is also available via the CPAN:

http://search.cpan.org/dist/Net-BGPdump/


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires the presense of libbgpdump.


